OL,3,CWarning over social media trend seeing
OL,4,C'pigeons injured with catapults'
OL,6,FA wildlife charity in Tewkesbury is
OL,7,Fcalling for the sale of sling shots
OL,8,Fand catapults to be banned for the
OL,9,Funder 18s amid a worrying new social
OL,10,Fmedia trend.
OL,12,FVale Wildlife Hospital and
OL,13,FRehabilitation Centre says it is
OL,14,Fhaving to treat a number of animals,
OL,15,Fmainly pigeons, who have been injured
OL,16,Fby young children using the weapons.
OL,18,FAt least one pigeon has died as a
OL,19,Fresult of its injuries, the charity
OL,20,Fhas warned.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/4
