PN,43102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1773667693
OL,3,CWarning over social media trend seeing
OL,4,C'pigeons injured with catapults'
OL,6,FThe charity says that youngsters are
OL,7,Ffilming themselves using the weapons
OL,8,Fand then posting the videos on social
OL,9,Fmedia.
OL,11,FNatalie Gould is one of the managers
OL,12,Fat the centre. She said: "We are one
OL,13,Fof the most disruptive species as
OL,14,Fhumans, but most of what we do is
OL,15,Findirectly impacting wildlife, such as
OL,16,Fbuilding work or hitting something on
OL,17,Fthe road, we don't do it intentionally.
OL,26,@tD@ZOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/4
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1773667693
OL,3,CWarning over social media trend seeing
OL,4,C'pigeons injured with catapults'
OL,6,F"So to see people are intentionally
OL,7,Fhurting these animals, it's very
OL,8,Ffrustrating, very upsetting and this
OL,9,Fis the youth, the next generation,
OL,10,Fwhich is meant to be looking after
OL,11,Fwildlife, so it's very concerning."
OL,13,FVale Wildlife Hospital and
OL,14,FRehabilitation Centre is now joining
OL,15,Fforces with other rescue centres in
OL,16,FGloucestershire to call on a ban of
OL,17,Fthe sale of sling shots and catapults
OL,18,Fto anyone under-18.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@cO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/4
