FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1773667693
OL,3,CWarning over social media trend seeing
OL,4,C'pigeons injured with catapults'
OL,6,FThey believe the move would
OL,7,Fdrastically cut the number of attacks
OL,8,Fon animals.
OL,10,FMs Gould said: "We're working very
OL,11,Fclosely with Naturewatch Foundation,
OL,12,Fthe wildlife charity in Cheltenham,
OL,13,Fthey are working really hard and have
OL,14,Forganised a coalition to campaign for
OL,15,Fan age restriction for the sale of
OL,16,Fthese weapons, because that's what
OL,17,Fthey are, they are being used as
OL,18,Fweapons."
OL,26,@rD@POUzD@IO]
